Flame 0.9.0:
    - new module - strings
    - string concatation with += or strings.concat(s1, s2)
    - new module system
    - borrow checker:
        - one owner:
            i32* a = 3;
            i32* b = a;
            print(a); // <- a no longer exist, its moved to b
        - ref is readonly:
            i32* a = 3;
            i32* a = ref a; // <- readonly
        